                </div>
                <div class="spec-item" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
                    <span class="label">Cloud & MLOps</span>
                    <h3>Deployment & Infrastructure</h3>
                    <p class="desc">Cloud platforms and MLOps tools to host, scale, and monitor production ML systems.</p>
                    <div class="tag-container">
                        <span class="tag">AWS</span>
                        <span class="tag">GCP</span>
                        <span class="tag">Docker</span>
                        <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
                        <span class="tag">DVC</span>
                        <span class="tag">GitHub Actions</span>
                        <span class="tag">Evidently AI</span>
                        <span class="tag">Apache Spark</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PAGE: EXPERIENCE -->
        <div id="page-deployments" class="page-view">
            <div style="min-height: 40vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; padding-bottom: 50px;">
                <h1>Experience<br>& Impact.</h1>
                <p class="punchline">A track record of measurable results across professional roles and research.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px;">

                <div class="metric-block">
                    <span class="label">Data Scientist @ Charity Staffing Inc. · 2025–Present</span>
                    <div class="spec-grid">
                        <div>
                            <span class="metric-value">35<span style="font-size:0.5em;vertical-align:top;">%</span></span>
                            <h3>Preprocessing Time Reduced.</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="desc">Engineered a distributed forecasting pipeline using Apache Spark and XGBoost/SARIMA ensemble, reducing forecast error from 13% to 8% MAPE. Built Spark workflows integrating six data sources and a FastAPI resource simulation tool deployed on GCP supporting a $4.5M grant renewal.</p>
                            <div class="tag-container">
                                <span class="tag">Apache Spark</span>
                                <span class="tag">XGBoost</span>
                                <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
                                <span class="tag">GCP</span>
                            </div>
                            <StarButton onclick="triggerCopilot('Deep dive into the Charity Staffing architecture.', 'charity')" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="metric-block">
                    <span class="label">Data Scientist @ Arizona State University · 2024–2025</span>
                    <div class="spec-grid">
                        <div>
                            <span class="metric-value">93<span style="font-size:0.5em;vertical-align:top;">%</span></span>
                            <h3>Classification Accuracy.</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="desc">Implemented Vision Transformer (ViT-B/16) in PyTorch achieving 93% top-1 accuracy on 60K medical video frames, outperforming ResNet-50 by 7%. Built NLP pipeline using BERT embeddings to map 12K transcripts to clinical taxonomy. NIH-funded project.</p>
                            <div class="tag-container">
                                <span class="tag">Vision Transformer</span>
                                <span class="tag">PyTorch</span>
                                <span class="tag">BERT</span>
                                <span class="tag">NLP</span>
                            </div>
                            <StarButton onclick="triggerCopilot('Explain the ASU Vision Transformer and NLP pipeline.', 'asu')" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="metric-block" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);">
                    <span class="label">Software Engineer @ ArcSoftech · 2020–2023</span>
                    <div class="spec-grid">
                        <div>
                            <span class="metric-value">50<span style="font-size:0.5em;vertical-align:top;">k+</span></span>
                            <h3>Daily Transactions.</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="desc">Designed Hadoop-based batch ingestion workflows processing 50K+ daily records. Reduced reporting latency from 15 minutes to under 3 minutes by rewriting log parsing scripts. Maintained 99.8% uptime for production data services.</p>
