                            <p class="desc">A production-grade ML pipeline for credit card fraud detection on 284,807 real transactions. Features DVC data versioning, MLflow experiment tracking on DagsHub, SMOTE for class imbalance, SHAP explainability, drift monitoring with Evidently AI, and a live FastAPI inference server — all wired into a full CI/CD pipeline via GitHub Actions.</p>

                            <div class="stat-mini-grid">
                                <div class="stat-mini">
